title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) per capita in Romania 2024
yAxis: GDP per capita in U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, containing a total of 41 data points.
Overall GDP per capita in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2006 and 2007.
Maximum GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, about 17685.87 was reported at Year 2024
The lowest GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, of value 853.11 was reported at Year 1992
